casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Donald Wayne BARNES, III, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 158274
COA: 337113 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 25, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the May 8, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
